caption.p: Cross-reactivity test of the novel DENV RT-LAMP assay to other human viruses. About 1620 RNA copies (33.6 PFU) of DENV-1 was used as the positive control. Testing viruses included Zika, Yellow fever virus, Adenovirus, Enterovirus, Influenza A and B viruses, Parainfluenza viruses 3, HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, and rhinovirus. NTC, no template control.
